                        <interp inst="t18420131-636-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 17.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy.</hi>—
<rs id="t18420131-636-punishment-26" type="punishmentDescription">
